{"id": 432, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最讨厌的聊天法是？", "description": "多次故事（or事故）告诉我们：有些人头像一闪准没好事。", "record_count": 7997, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071944462PUZXeazQSgY9Gk8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-24T12:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 4588, "content": "发了信息一直不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147348}, {"id": 4589, "content": "每次都“亲”前“亲”后的 像某宝客服似的 这小广告也是这样贴的吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 4591, "content": "滚", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128838}, {"id": 4592, "content": "一会说", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147381}, {"id": 4593, "content": "我去洗澡了，我去吃饭了，我在听课，我在开会。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 44037}, {"id": 4594, "content": "test\r\n", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235040n6sbVP1Sj0mEQAIT.jpg", "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850}, {"id": 4595, "content": "一长段的语音，要发那么多语音请打电话好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 65078}, {"id": 4619, "content": "好", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147467}, {"id": 4649, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147534}, {"id": 4742, "content": "最讨厌的聊天方式，查你祖宗十八代", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147553}, {"id": 5245, "content": "我出一堆问号，你答一个句号， 我再出一堆问号，你再答一个句号……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147567}, {"id": 5250, "content": "发各种图片回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147749}, {"id": 4932, "content": "明白说了，不见面不约泡，却依旧不死心的！真让人心烦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147592}, {"id": 5105, "content": "hh", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147673}, {"id": 5027, "content": "发了紧急的消息，没有回，结果在朋友圈发现ta点赞了别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147619}, {"id": 5078, "content": "-我起床了\n-我吃饭了\n-我睡了\n\n听你汇报你作息有病啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147652}, {"id": 4641, "content": "总是等着你先说话，要是不说就觉得你不在意她，你要是在意我你也会跟我先说话的", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145575}, {"id": 4642, "content": "当我先找你然后说想你的时候，你的回答确是原来你这么爱我啊？靠～", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145575}, {"id": 4643, "content": "明明主动找的你却同时和另一个人聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145575}, {"id": 5435, "content": "回复从不超过五个字／永远只说自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 5438, "content": "对方一个字的回复都能换来你数倍的回复，多出来的不是废话就是爱！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147924}, {"id": 5439, "content": "对方一个字的回复都能换来你数倍的回复，多出来的不是废话就是爱！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147924}, {"id": 5710, "content": "啥\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148438}, {"id": 5261, "content": "聊着聊着没人了，还有不熟的人偏偏装作很熟的样子一直扯?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146065}, {"id": 5277, "content": "每一次找我说话只有倾泻负能量", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131311}, {"id": 5378, "content": "30--60分钟后回复我.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147849}, {"id": 5370, "content": "很久没联系过的人：记得我是谁吗，猜猜看——我猜你妹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130404}, {"id": 5804, "content": "各种社交软件都玩玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148758}, {"id": 5808, "content": "……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145974}, {"id": 5831, "content": "恩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142257}, {"id": 5511, "content": "沉浸在自己的世界，根本不接我的话，那你干嘛和我聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142779}, {"id": 5515, "content": "说三字以内的话故意加个句号。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118123}, {"id": 5731, "content": "说了也么多，你们不也是这样吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148458}, {"id": 5736, "content": "哦\n嗯\n呵呵\n好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148500}, {"id": 5850, "content": "讨厌只见过一两次的上来就问在干嘛，好想回关你屁事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121890}, {"id": 5856, "content": "在微信群里说了话，没一个人回应", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148973}, {"id": 5986, "content": "问答是聊天…", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234822xUSHL9gVZ1fEADB5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116782}, {"id": 4608, "content": "标点符号发过来，让我无话可说", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110781}, {"id": 21249, "content": "“在干嘛？”每次都恨不得回一句：在干你（无论对方男女，ps俺是女生）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276056}, {"id": 4610, "content": "你在睡觉，你在洗澡，你在外面，你不方便回我，可你哪来的时间发上千字的说说！", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138553}, {"id": 4611, "content": "加油", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6411, "content": "?讨厌这个表情的举爪", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151061}, {"id": 4624, "content": "聊天感觉都对了，一表白都废了，放下各种桃花只为你，你却把我当桃核", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147471}, {"id": 4626, "content": "嗯嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 67481}, {"id": 18706, "content": "………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 7700, "content": "你加的我你不告诉我是谁，好几天以后问我一句我叫啥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158342}, {"id": 7445, "content": "在群里问了一个问题，等了很久也没人回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156273}, {"id": 7701, "content": "俩人不认识，空间看完照片加你好友第一句话处么？看你照片第一眼就喜欢上你了，给你发一堆他自己认为帅的照片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158342}, {"id": 5654, "content": "美女，你有男朋友没？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143671}, {"id": 7452, "content": "。。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142894}]}